CONTRIBUTING.md
     1в†’# Contributing
     3в†’1. [Fork it](https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo/)
     4в†’2. Install dependencies (`npm install`)
     5в†’3. Create your feature branch (`git checkout -b my-new-feature`)
     6в†’4. Commit your changes (`git commit -am 'Added some feature'`)
     7в†’5. Test your changes (`npm test`)
     8в†’6. Push to the branch (`git push origin my-new-feature`)
     9в†’7. [Create new Pull Request](https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request/)
    10в†’
    11в†’## Testing
    13в†’We use [TAP](https://github.com/tapjs/node-tap) to write tests. Run our test suite with this command:
    14в†’
    15в†’```
    16в†’npm test
    17в†’```
    18в†’
    19в†’## Code Style
    21в†’We use [standard](https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard) and [editorconfig](http://editorconfig.org) to maintain code style and best practices. Please make sure your PR adheres to the guides by running:
    22в†’
    23в†’```
    24в†’npm run lint
    25в†’```
